Package HumanObject.Administrator

Class Administrator

java.lang.Object
HumanObject.BasePerson
HumanObject.Administrator.Administrator
public class Administrator extends BasePerson
The Administrator class represents an administrator entity, which extends the BasePerson class. It includes methods for managing patients and staff, and handles ID generation for administrator objects.

      public Administrator()
      Default constructor that initializes an Administrator object. The ID is auto-incremented based on lastID. The role is set to ROLE.ADMINISTRATOR.

    • Administrator

      public Administrator(String Name, Date DOB, Boolean Gender)
      Constructor used for creating an Administrator object and adding it to the text file HMS.txt. The role is set to ROLE.ADMINISTRATOR.
      Parameters:
      Name - The name of the administrator.
      DOB - The date of birth of the administrator.
      Gender - The gender of the administrator. True for male, False for female.
